% ============================================================================
% SUMMARY CHECKLIST
% ============================================================================

Before finishing architecture.json and .pddrc generation:

**Common checks (both styles):**
□ Every filename uses underscores, NO slashes
□ Every filename ends with valid PascalCase language suffix
□ Every filepath matches framework/project conventions
□ Verified paths using Python script or dry-run

**Style 1 checks (per-module exact paths — Next.js/Nuxt/SvelteKit):**
□ Every module has a dedicated context in .pddrc
□ Each context's `paths:` pattern matches its basename
□ Each context's `outputs.code.path` matches its filepath exactly
□ `prompts_dir` appears ONLY in `default` context
□ All prompt files are FLAT in `prompts/` directory

**Style 2 checks (template-based group contexts — Python/Go/Rust):**
□ Modules are grouped by output directory into group contexts
□ Each group context has `generate_output_path` set to the directory
□ Each group context has `prompts_dir` pointing to its subdirectory (e.g., `"prompts/backend"`)
□ All prompt files are in the group's `prompts_dir` subdirectory
□ No `outputs.code.path` on group contexts (template expansion handles it)
